Leemos datos y agregamos Interpretaci√≥n de Estatus

base<-read.csv("../data/UIID_20190201.csv",header=T)
# class(base)
base01<-base%>%
  as_data_frame()%>%
  select(gruposos,grupodx)%>%
  filter(grupodx!=0)
# class(base01)
base01

Distribuci√≥n por grupo diag√≥stico

gg01<-ggplot(base01, aes(x=factor(1), fill=gruposos))+
  geom_bar(width = 1)+
  coord_polar("y")
gg01

gb01<-base01%>%
  group_by(gruposos)%>%
  summarise(n_px=n(),
            per_px=round(n_px/nrow(.),4),
            porcentaje= paste0(formatC(100 * per_px, digits = 2, format = "f"), "%"))%>%
  rename(Grupo=gruposos)
gb01
## Create a basic bar
pie00 <- ggplot(gb01, aes(x="", y=n_px, fill=Grupo)) + geom_bar(stat="identity", width=1)+
  coord_polar("y", start=0) + geom_text(aes(label = n_px), position = position_stack(vjust = 0.5),size=2) +
  scale_fill_manual(values=c("#55DDE0", "#33658A", "#2F4858", "#F6AE2D", "#F26419", "#999999","#CC6666", "#9999CC", "#66CC99")) +
  labs(x = NULL, y = NULL, fill = NULL, title = "Grupos Diagn√≥sticos (n)")+
  theme_classic() + theme(axis.line = element_blank(),
          axis.text = element_blank(),
          axis.ticks = element_blank(),
          plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, color = "#666666"))
pie00

## Create a basic bar
pie<- ggplot(gb01, aes(x="", y=per_px, fill=Grupo)) + geom_bar(stat="identity", width=1)
# pie
## Convert to pie (polar coordinates) and add labels
pie <- pie+coord_polar("y", start=0) + geom_text(aes(label = paste0(round(per_px*100,4), "%")), position = position_stack(vjust = 0.5),size=2)

# pie
## Add color scale (hex colors)
pie<-pie + scale_fill_manual(values=c("#55DDE0", "#33658A", "#2F4858", "#F6AE2D", "#F26419", "#999999","#CC6666", "#9999CC", "#66CC99")) 
# pie
# Remove labels and add title
pie<-pie + labs(x = NULL, y = NULL, fill = NULL, title = "Grupos Diagn√≥sticos (%)")
# pie
## Tidy up the theme
pie <- pie + theme_classic() + theme(axis.line = element_blank(),
          axis.text = element_blank(),
          axis.ticks = element_blank(),
          plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, color = "#666666"))
pie
